metadata.name: Unravel People's MEEBITS
metadata.description: Abbreviation for unravel people's MEEBITS, which represents an inactive state of pMEEBITS. Users can participate in a new Meebit acquirement subscription and will receive unravel people's MEEBITS as credit. upMEEBITS can be claimed into pMEEBITS when the subscription successfully acquires a new Meebit.
